{"tid":805221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英：體育界沒有經濟貢獻","createTime":"2018-09-03T15:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T17:49:41.000Z","uid":47359,"like":11,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6e5f960bf2fadfef8c7ec6c0c960d88fc75d3e8e","tid":805221,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:07:43.000Z","msg":"梁振英：宗教界、體育界沒有經濟貢獻 (18:33)<br />\n2014/10/25<br />\n<br />\n 共1幅  上一頁下一頁 <br />\n特首梁振英今日會見傳媒時，為提名委員會制度護航。他稱，提委會需要均衝參與，並舉例指無論佔本港經濟來源16%的金融界，還是體育界、宗教界這些「沒有任何經濟貢獻」的界別，亦可以參與提名。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁振英是在參加2014年仁川亞洲殘疾人運動會港隊歡迎儀式時見記者，並強調提名委員會需要均衡參與，他指自己曾多次跟傳媒表示，提委會不應向任何階層傾斜，他舉例指有些界別「沒有任何經濟貢獻」，例如體育界、宗教界等，也能夠參與提名。<br />\n<br />\n(即時新聞)"},{"pid":"00bfd26875b920afecabfcafc696b51b67ec9f75","tid":805221,"uid":2436,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:08:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40fca9b7d05ada3f79f60d72c241a2233d98d932","tid":805221,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:09:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79e06301ce647739c4a1566f0eafe837d23ac0d6","tid":805221,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"40fca9b7d05ada3f79f60d72c241a2233d98d932","tid":805221,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:09:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:09:50.000Z","msg":"亞軍嘛"},{"pid":"8b15ac5a28ab58d94002fa0c78a6041a0241d95a","tid":805221,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"40fca9b7d05ada3f79f60d72c241a2233d98d932","tid":805221,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:09:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:10:06.000Z","msg":"亞運嘛"},{"pid":"ec7c8fb8f598fc4728234f1366fcd69e6c37b92d","tid":805221,"uid":69213,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:10:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5e13aa638d42340d3b2f44c44a325f4d6370bbe","tid":805221,"uid":